These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-3-1::.
4 different games are played: domino, poker, backgammon, billiard
There 4 different types of food: apple, banana, grapes, pineapple
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, august, november, december
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, ship, tram, van
 1. the person eating banana is on the left or right of the person driving the ship##3
 2. the person playing poker is the person eating pineapple##1
 3. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person playing poker##1
 5. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the person eating grapes is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in june##3
 7. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the person playing poker##1
 8. the person playing billiard is on the right of the person eating grapes##1
 9. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far left##1
10. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
11. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person playing domino##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2      |      3      |   4   |
| Game    | backgammon   | poker       | domino | billiard   |
| Food        | banana    | pineapple  | grapes      | apple |
| Birthday         | december      | august | november         | june   |
| Transport   | quad-bike | ship       | tram        | van   |

