3. the photographer is the person watching scientific movies##1
4. the person watching satire movies is on the far left##1
5. the person traveling to hamburg is the person watching scientific movies##1
6. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the far left or far right##3
7. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
8. the videographer is between the person drinking lemonade and the person traveling to venice##2
9. the librarian is on the left or right of the person drinking soy-milk##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |     3     |      4       |
| Job           | lawyer     | videographer | librarian | photographer |
| Movie-Genre   | satire     | family       | epic      | scientific   |
| City   | san-francisco   | boston   | venice    | hamburg       |
| Beverage           | lemonade | juice        | fanta    | soy-milk        |

