.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-3-5::.
House: palace, modern, craftsman, gothic-revival
There 4 different types of food: carrot, kiwi, pineapple, zucchini
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: funk, metal, reggae, trance
There are 4 different favourite colors: ivory, turquise, coral, emerald
 1. the person who likes ivory is on the left or right of the person eating kiwi##3
 2. the person eating zucchini is on the left or right of the person eating carrot##3
 3. the palace house is on the left of the person eating pineapple##1
 4. the person eating zucchini is on the right of the person eating carrot##1
 5. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the person who likes emerald##1
 6. the gothic-revival house is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the fan of funk is on the left or right of the person eating zucchini##3
 8. the craftsman house is on the left of the person eating kiwi##1
 9. the person eating pineapple is on the left of the person who likes turquise##1
10. the fan of trance is between the palace house and the fan of reggae##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |     3     |     4      |
| House      | gothic-revival | palace | craftsman     | modern       |
| Food          | carrot   | zucchini    | pineapple | kiwi       |
| Music-Genre   | funk     | metal       | trance    | reggae     |
| Color         | coral  | emerald  | ivory | turquise |

