 8. the fan of gospel is the person driving the snowmobile##1
 9. the fan of electronic is on the left or right of the person traveling to rome##3
10. the person drinking fanta is on the far right##1
11. the fan of disco is the person traveling to rome##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |   2    |      3      |     4      |
