 7. the egyptian is between the person who's sport is parkour and the pakistani##2
 8. the fan of pop is the bongani-smoker##1
 9. the fan of gospel is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1
10. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left or right of the siglo-smoker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3     |      4       |
| Cigar         | ritmeester | siglo     | bluemaster  | bongani |
