The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: zombie, western, animation, family
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, dog, fish, pony
4 different games are played: mah-jongg, domino, whist, scrabble
 1. the owner of the pony is the person playing scrabble##1
 2. the person watching zombie movies is between the owner of the dog and the owner of the pony##2
 3. the owner of the fish is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 4. the owner of the fish is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
 5. the person playing scrabble is the owner of the pony##1
 6. the person who's hobby is dancing is between the person playing whist and the person who's hobby is writing##2
 7. the person who's hobby is dancing is the person playing mah-jongg##1
 8. the owner of the fish is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
 9. the person watching family movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##3
10. the person playing whist is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
11. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left or right of the person watching family movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |    2     |      3       |       4       |
| Hobby   | writing    | dancing  | sudoku       | magic-tricks  |
| Movie-Genre     | western    | zombie | animation | family        |
| Pet     | pony       | fish     | dog          | chinchilla    |
| Game   | scrabble | mah-jongg    | whist     | domino |

