 6. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left of the australian##1
 7. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the canadian##1
 8. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 9. the australian is the person who growssunflower##1
10. the polish is on the left or right of the person who growsdaisy##3
11. the person watching zombie movies is the person who's hobby is chess##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |      3       |     4     |
| Hobby         | chess      | video-games | sudoku       | drawing   |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie     | documentary | martial-arts | animation |
| Flower   | daffodil    | daisy     | amaryllis        | sunflower       |
| Nationality     | pakistani | canadian   | polish   | australian       |

