.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-3-20::.
There 4 different types of food: artichoke, blueberry, radish, watermelon
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, aristoff, vegafina, baccarat
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, comedy, mystery, satire
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daisy, orchid, lily, poppy
 1. the person eating artichoke is on the far right##1
 2. the person who growsorchid is on the right of the havana-smoker##1
 3. the person eating blueberry is on the left of the person eating watermelon##1
 4. the aristoff-smoker is between the person who growslily and the person who growsorchid##2
 5. the person watching adventure movies is on the left or right of the person eating radish##3
 6. the person watching adventure movies is between the aristoff-smoker and the person who growsdaisy##2
 7. the person watching mystery movies is the baccarat-smoker##1
 8. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person watching satire movies##1
 9. the person eating radish is the aristoff-smoker##1
10. the person watching adventure movies is the vegafina-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |    3     |     4     |
| Food          | blueberry | watermelon   | radish   | artichoke |
| Cigar           | havana   | vegafina     | aristoff   | baccarat |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy    | adventure    | satire   | mystery   |
| Flower         | daisy    | orchid | poppy | lily    |

 